    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for Model Risk Level 3. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted based on the quasi-static nature of the COU, the conservative ASTM F1717 load rate, and the corroborating multi-laboratory experimental dataset. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified <10% relative error and E/uval < 1.96 acceptance bounds. The credibility package is assessed as sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
